{"tid":438403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一日兩電騙 兩大學生共失11.5萬人仔","createTime":"2017-10-17T01:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T05:03:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"42d2d9d4663914a4dedf14cb790200e96249c80b","tid":438403,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"屯門屯安里一單位，昨晚9時許，一名18歲姓韓內地女大學生報警稱，昨早接獲一名自稱大陸出入境部門的不明男子來電，指她與一宗刑事案件有關，電話其後轉駁至另一名不明男子，聲稱為內地執法人員，要求她將8萬元人民幣存入兩個內地戶口。<br />\n<br />\n女大學生按指示存款後懷疑受騙。案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由屯門警區刑事調查跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，上水一鳴路一單位，一名24歲姓譚內地女大學生，昨早亦接獲一名自稱上海公安的不明男子來電，指她與一宗刑事案件有關，要求她將約3萬5千元人民幣分別存入兩個內地戶口。<br />\n<br />\n女大學生按指示存款後懷疑受騙，於是報案。案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由大埔警區刑事調查跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57341041&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57341041%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171017&d=4r1OJhd6hxEzagf6THXhUDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e073a321\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57341041%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171017&h=8a8db156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57341041&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171017</a>"},{"pid":"2dacd5db5ad92107b410aa877cc41eae6de4c62c","tid":438403,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:41:17.000Z","msg":"大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe3aa4970410f2bae8f4e3daedea8116dcbcb3b","tid":438403,"uid":63909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:42:23.000Z","msg":"兩內地女大學生呀<br />\n屌你<br />\n個標題咁撚誤導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400f58026e75cb5d0fbe2e1639ecd58bb41eb741","tid":438403,"ui